<front>
<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Johann II. von Nassau-Wiesbaden-Idstein, Erzbischof von Mainz, Johann II. von Brunn, Bischof von Würzburg, Leonhard, Graf von Castell, Konrad IV. Schenk von Limpurg, Johann II., Graf von Wertheim, Thomas, Graf von Rieneck, Konrad IX. von Weinsberg, Erbkämmerer des Reichs, Konrad VI. von Bickenbach, Burggraf von Miltenberg, Hanneman Echter von Mespelbrunn, Viztum zu Aschaffenburg, und Arnold von Seckendorff, Amtmann zu Neustadt an der Aisch</head><p>Der Rat bittet um Geleit für Nürnberger Bürger und Kaufleute auf dem Weg zu und von der Frankfurter Herbstmesse.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_42" id="20r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_42_r2l1"><expan>No<ex>ta</ex></expan> Geleytſbrief in die <expan>frankfurt<ex>er</ex></expan> herbſtmeſſe etc </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_42_r2l2"><expan>no<ex>ta</ex></expan> Byſſchof cʒu Meincʒ </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_42_r2l3">Byſſchof ʒu <expan>vvircʒb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_42_r2l4"><expan>Lynharte<ex>n</ex></expan> Grafen vnd <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> cʒu Caſtell </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_42_r2l5"><expan>Conr<ex>ad</ex></expan> Schenken <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> cʒu <expan>Lymp<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_42_r2l6">Graf Johanſen von wertheim </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_42_r2l7"><expan>No<ex>ta</ex></expan> Graf Thoman von Ryneck </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_42_r2l10"><expan>no<ex>ta</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>Conr<ex>ad</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> ʒu <expan>vveinſp<ex>er</ex>g</expan> des <expan>heilige<ex>n</ex></expan> Reichs ErbCamermeiſter </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_42_r2l12">
<del rend="strikethrough"><expan>no<ex>ta</ex></expan></del> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>Conr<ex>ad</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> cʒu Pickenbach vnd <expan>Burggr<ex>af</ex></expan> cʒu <expan>Mıltemb<ex>er</ex>g</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_42_r2l13"><expan>no<ex>ta</ex></expan> <expan>ha<ex>n</ex>man</expan> Echter vicʒtum cʒu Aſchaffemburg </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_42_r2l15"><expan>Arnolte<ex>n</ex></expan> von Seckendorff Amptman cʒu der <expan>Newe<ex>n</ex>ſtat</expan> an <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> Eyſch </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><pb facs="#facs_42"/>
<ab facs="#facs_42_r2l16">Gnediger herre VVir bitten ewr <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> mit <expan>alle<ex>m</ex></expan> fleiſʒ . daʒ 
<del rend="strikethrough">Jr </del> ewr </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_42_r2l17">gnade <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> burger vnd kaufflewte vnd auch Jr habe vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_42_r2l18">kauffmanſchaft vnd die Jren in die <expan>nehſtkunftige<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>frankfurt<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_42_r2l19">herbſmeſſe . vnd wider darauſʒ mit geleyte <expan>gnedıklıch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_42_r2l20"><expan>fürſeh<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wölle . Alſo . vvenn ſıe oder die Jren darümb cʒu <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_42_r2l21">gnaden 
<del rend="strikethrough">k </del> oder aber ~ den ewrn <expan>kume<ex>n</ex></expan> vnd des begern . daʒ ſie </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_42_r2l22">
<del rend="strikethrough"><expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan></del> vnd das Jr <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> durch ewr lande herſchäfft vnd gepyte </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_42_r2l25">ſicher geleẏtet werden / Als etc das <expan>wolle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc vnd biten 
<add><ab facs="#facs_42_line_1577009532607_1481">auch </ab></add> des </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_42_r2l26">ewr gnedig <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>Antvv<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> wıder beẏ diſem <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> dyener </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_42_r2l28"><expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>fe<ex>ri</ex>a</expan> ıj̃ <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> petri ad <expan>vinc<ex>u</ex>la</expan> . Anno etc xix<hi rend="sup">no</hi></ab>
<note place="bottomcentral">
<ab facs="#facs_42_r2l29"><expan>No<ex>ta</ex></expan> <expan>cuil<ex>ibet</ex></expan> <expan>mutat<ex>is</ex></expan> <expan>mutand<ex>is</ex></expan> </ab>
</note>
<note place="marginleft">
<ab facs="#facs_42_r2l31"><expan>No<ex>ta</ex></expan> <expan>Officialib<ex>us</ex></expan> ſic . </ab>
</note>
<ab facs="#facs_42_r2l30">VVenn ſie oder die Jren darümb cʒu euch <expan>kume<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_42_r2l32">vnd des begern / daʒ Jr 
<add><ab facs="#facs_42_line_1577009562062_1507"><expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab></add> ſie vnd das Jr durch ewr </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_42_r2l33">gepyete <expan>alſu<ex>er</ex>re</expan> Jr cʒugeleyten habt / ſicher geleiten </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_42_r2l34">wollet Als etc Das <expan>wolle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc <expan>Antvv<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> etc </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_42" id="20r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>
<expan>No<ex>ta</ex></expan> geleytsbrief in die
                            <expan>Frankfurt<ex>er</ex></expan> herbstmesse
                                etc.<lb/><expan>No<ex>ta</ex></expan> Bysschof czu
                        Meincz<lb/>Bysschof zu
                                <expan>Wirczb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan><lb/><expan>Lynharte<ex>n</ex></expan>,
                        grafen und <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> czu
                                Castell<lb/><expan>Conr<ex>ad</ex></expan> Schenken,
                                <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> czu
                        <expan>Lymp<ex>ur</ex>g</expan><lb/>Graf Johansen von Wertheim<lb/>Graf
                        Thoman von Ryneck<lb/><expan>No<ex>ta</ex></expan>
<expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Conr<ex>ad</ex></expan>, <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> zu
                                <expan>Weinsp<ex>er</ex>g</expan>, des
                            <expan>heilige<ex>n</ex></expan> reichs
                                erbcamermeister<lb/><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Conr<ex>ad</ex></expan>, <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> czu
                        Pickenbach und <expan>burggr<ex>af</ex></expan> czu
                                <expan>Miltemb<ex>er</ex>g</expan><lb/><expan>No<ex>ta</ex></expan>
<expan>Ha<ex>n</ex>man</expan> echter, vicztum czu
                                Aschaffemburg<lb/><expan>Arnolte<ex>n</ex></expan> von Seckendorff,
                        amptman czu der <expan>Newe<ex>n</ex>stat</expan> an
                            <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> Eysch </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab><pb facs="#facs_42"/>Gnediger herre, wir bitten ewr <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> mit
                <expan>alle<ex>m</ex></expan> fleisz, daz ewr gnade <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
            burger und kaufflewte und auch ir habe und kauffmanschaft und die iren in die
                <expan>nehstkunftige<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>Frankfurt<ex>er</ex></expan> herbsmesse und wider darausz mit geleyte
                <expan>gnediklich<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>fürseh<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wölle. Also wenn sie oder die iren darümb czu
                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> gnaden oder aber den ewrn <expan>kume<ex>n</ex></expan>
            und des begern, daz sie und das ir <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> durch ewr lande
            herschäfft und gepyte sicher geleytet werden als etc. Das <expan>wolle<ex>n</ex></expan>
            etc. Und biten <add>auch</add> des ewr gnedig
              <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>antw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> wider bey disem <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan> dyener.
                <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>fe<ex>ri</ex>a</expan> ii <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> Petri ad
                <expan>vinc<ex>u</ex>la</expan> anno etc. xix<hi rend="sup">no</hi>. <app>
<note place="bottomcentral">
<expan>No<ex>ta</ex></expan>
<expan>cuil<ex>ibet</ex></expan>
<expan>mutat<ex>is</ex></expan>
<expan>mutand<ex>is</ex></expan>. </note>
</app><app>
<note place="marginleft">
<expan>No<ex>ta</ex></expan>
<expan>officialib<ex>us</ex></expan> sic. </note>
</app>Wenn sie oder die iren darümb czu euch <expan>kume<ex>n</ex></expan> und des
            begern, daz ir <add><expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan></add> sie und das ir durch ewr gepyete
                <expan>alsv<ex>er</ex>re</expan> ir czu geleyten habt, sicher geleiten wollet, als
            etc. Das <expan>wolle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc. <expan>Antw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> etc. </ab></div>
</div></body>
</text>
